videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield finds Megan Walker, who knocks down a 3 from the corner.
videos.headline: Walker nails corner 3

videos.description: UConn loses control of the ball, but Olivia Nelson-Ododa gets it right back when Houston loses control, and finishes with a layup.
videos.headline: Nelson-Ododa steals, makes layup
